          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悄焚香，春怨虑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "教我惜春无计。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "短叹长吁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘琴音缭乱，必然又有什么心事。待我来将她打断。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，明日乃是饯花之期，姑娘你该休养休养才是呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉惊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，就要送春了么！"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春去了，它还来是不来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春去无言，我哪儿知道哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春光既去，花事阑珊。你与我收拾花锄、花囊，明日好去葬花，了此一春光景。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，似水流年，今果如此，杜丽娘有词伤春，我岂得无词寄兴，待我来题诗一"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "首！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉研磨，蘸笔，沉思。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "侬今制就送春词，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望春归兮是何时！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "未死春蚕忍断丝！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉起身。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，身体困乏，不免稍睡一时。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "风竹萧萧，悄无人语。想是林妹妹春困未醒，待我偷看片时，免得扰她清梦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉翻身卧被坐床。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日价情思睡昏昏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉掀帘笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为什么情思睡昏昏？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉惊羞，举被掩面倒身伪睡，贾宝玉坐床，推林黛玉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹，你为何不理我呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鹦鹉传呼，想是宝二爷来啦，待我进去看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊二爷，姑娘现在酣睡，你有话，等她起来再说吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉翻身坐起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个睡觉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我当是姑娘睡着了哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉理发。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我正要睡觉，你来此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给你个榧子吃，我都听见了啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷听见什么，可是我们姑娘叫我不是？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉摇首。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是，不是。快把你们的好茶倒与我喝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们这儿哪有什么好茶？您要好的，等袭人来吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休要理他，快去与我舀水。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他是客人，自然是先倒茶来，再给姑娘舀水呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉怒视。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讨厌！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃回顾。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这可怎么好！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃下。贾宝玉背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好丫头，我若得与你多情小姐同鸳帐，怎舍得叫你叠被铺床。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉推贾宝玉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二哥，你说些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉拉林黛玉手笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我无有说什么呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉以手掩面哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今是新兴头，听了村话来，也说给我听，看了混账书，也拿我取笑，我倒做"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了替爷们解闷的了。我去告诉舅父、舅母，评评此理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉惊阻林黛玉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好妹妹，不要如此，我再说这样话，教我嘴上长个疔疮，烂了舌头，一辈子不"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "能说话。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃捧茶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，这是何苦？无缘无故地，又来跟姑娘生气。袭人刚来找你，叫你快去换衣"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "裳，老爷叫你去哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你莫骗我，你不怕我去了，你家姑娘更要生气么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您快着点儿出去，茗烟在外头等着您哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃推贾宝玉，贾宝玉向内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要走了。紫鹃，你好好伺候姑娘，我去去就来，好与你家姑娘陪礼，免得她"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又要生气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，这是哪里说起！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才真是老爷叫二爷么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。姑娘不要跟二爷生气，待我就去与姑娘舀水。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "淘气的丫头，方才若不是你多嘴，哪里来的闲气，还不与我拿斗篷来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这般时候，姑娘要斗篷何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷呼唤二爷，不知为了何事，我要去探听探听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷刚说去去就来，外面风大，姑娘你不用去啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休要多言，快快与我取来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃取斗篷为林黛玉披上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明明的我与他心心相印，"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘回来还要抚琴吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我拿到院中，月光下等候姑娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "苦衷情无处诉留证无人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "待明朝收拾起瘗玉埋春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情种情根天造就，情天难补恨难平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉下。）"
        }
      ],
